Class ReferencedSoundSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eng.aisp.segmented.LabeledSegmentSpec
      • org.eng.aisp.dataset.ReferencedSoundSpec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IReferencedDataSpec<SoundRecording>, IReferencedSoundSpec
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MetaData.Record

    public class ReferencedSoundSpec
extends LabeledSegmentSpec
implements IReferencedSoundSpec
    A simple/obvious implementation of IReferencedSoundSpec. Uses a LabeledSegment to define the segment, if any, and and added reference field to hold the reference.
    Author:
    DavidWood
